         Okay the only thing that scares me about this post is that my gear at 56 is very much in line with what you want for your "short term" goals (I only recently started upgrading my equipment).</P><P>My only recommendation is level up, if you see a good deal buy it (wish I had the bazaar), you have plenty of gear to successfully take on what is out there.</P><P>To respond to your question, I just picked up a Terrorclaw Hide and it is very nice and very fun, highly recommended.  I would go Grey Flesh Gloves over Coldain Skin Gloves as well.  I think the short term goal items are very nice.</P><P>"And may thee farewell, wherever thy fare!<BR>Sislibik Underfoot<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=255911" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=255911</a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
