         gear is overrated. 90% of doing well as a necro is playing the class well, in terms of reactions, knowing game mechanics, and your classes capabilities.</P><P>Gear just makes things easier by giving you more efficiency and/or greater survivability when the shit hits the fan.</P><P>And that's it.. so don't sweat whether your gear isn't uber.</P><P><a href="http://tru7h.org/absor/" target="_blank">http://tru7h.org/absor/</a> -  ask absor anything!<BR><a href="http://xzzy.org/ereet/" target="_blank">http://xzzy.org/ereet/</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
