         My gear is UBER?  Look at <a href="http://www.tritonguild.com" target="_blank">www.tritonguild.com</a> if you want to see UBER!  I'm not even close.  Some of their Necros (Sallymander/Zaar) have over every resist triple digit, int/sta of over 200, 3000'ish hp and 4000'ish mana.  Some don't even equip their epic and prefer the SoSS.  Now THAT is UBER!</P><P>I'm nowhere near!  I did twink about 2k worth, but that not all that much really!  Sure I obviously got some good deals though!  Most of my money came from camping in the $$$ spots.  </P><P>12-15 OOT Little Sisters drop a 2pp belt every drop.<BR>18-24 Hermit drops FS weapons every 5th kill<BR>24-29 OOT One Named Sister drop a 12pp sword every kill<BR>36-38 Rangers/Druids drops gear worth between 3pp - 15pp a kill.</P><P>Its really not that hard to make money!  </P><P>You should be able to get at LEAST this by level 30:</P><P>Batfang Headband (3int)<BR>Golden Sapphire Ears (4int)<BR>Sheer Bone Mask (3int)<BR>Bracelets of Wooven Grass (3int and hp)<BR>Embroidered Black Cloth (shoulder slot hp and mana)<BR>Kunzar Cloak (2int)<BR>Shadowbound Gloves and Boots (glove give INT,STR mana: boots HP MANA)<BR>Dagger of Marnek (Range Int and Mana)<BR>Stein of Mogguk (10int)<BR>Dragoon Dirk or Needlite Stinger<BR>Advisor Robe or Oracle Robe</P><P>That should get you close to 200int.</P><P>I'd also recommend Velium Fire rings but they go for 400pp each.  They are the BEST investment though.  Higher recommended than EVERYTHING on the above list since HP are king.</P><P>Keep with it, hunt the Druids/Rangers in EC/WC at 36-39 and you'll be rich!  100pp an hour easy (more if you have some decent gear.)</P><P>Deedrok Out.</P><P></P><P><strong>Deedrok - Level 37<BR>  Necromancer of E'ci<BR>  <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234678" target="_blank">My Gear</a></strong><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
